Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • Request
      • View

  • public class View
extends Request
    View class - The View represents a user entered command or request. The View is used by the Controller to build a Session to store on the sessionStack. Collection of method to manage the view attributes. Extends Request class. ***********************************************************************************************************************
